Package neuralNetwork.neuralNetworkStructures

A package of FeedForwardNNs with different topographies.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
CompleteCheckersNN A constant NeuronLayer size Feed-Forward Neural Network without brain damage.
NeuralNetwork1L A simple Feed-Forward Neural Network with 1 hidden layer.
NeuralNetwork2L A Feed-Forward Neural Network with 2 hidden layers.
NeuralNetwork3L A Feed-Forward Neural Network with 5 hidden layers.
NeuralNetwork4L A Feed-Forward Neural Network with 4 hidden layers.
PyramidCheckersNN A Feed-Forward Neural Network without brain-damage that is constructed in a pyramid shape.
